Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Argentina invokes security pact
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvcy
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Apr 1982
Latest move leaves US in tricky situation, having to decide between two so-called allies. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less